de.unlixx.runpng.util

Class SortedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unlixx.runpng.util.SortedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The class type to sort.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class SortedList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>
    A generic sorted list, which sorts it's elements while adding. It implements the Iterable interface in order to be used in a lambda style "for (x : y) loop".
